{"id":48406,"date":"2024-02-16T09:50:00","date_gmt":"2024-02-16T04:20:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=48406"},"modified":"2023-08-23T18:04:42","modified_gmt":"2023-08-23T12:34:42","slug":"importance-of-kitchen-backsplash-tile","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/importance-of-kitchen-backsplash-tile\/","title":{"rendered":"5 Reasons Why Your Home Needs a Kitchen Backsplash Tile Now!"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>A kitchen backsplash tile is the need of the hour. Read more about their versatile functionality and designs.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;ve ever been in a spot where the food from your pressure cooker has splattered all over the place, you know the importance of a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-backsplash-ideas\/\">kitchen backsplash<\/a> tile. Because no one needs to see the gravy marks from last night&#8217;s curry. A tile backsplash brings more than just aesthetic value to your kitchen. It adds a protective functional cover to the beautiful walls that you so painstakingly matched with the scheme of your home.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Gone are the days of mismatched tiles with over-the-top prints that made your kitchen look like a painting from the 90s. Today you can choose from a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/modular-kitchen-colour-combinations\/\">range of colour palettes<\/a> and designs that make a statement while retaining the theme of your home. But looks are just one of its benefits. Here&#8217;s why every kitchen needs a backsplash tile.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Easy Cleaning Backsplash Tiles&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Indian cuisine is an amalgamation of spices and condiments that infuse flavour into the dish. The whiff of a fresh dal <em>tadka<\/em> can fill the house with an aroma that will tantalise your senses but also leave nasty splatters on the wall. This beautiful printed backsplash tile ensures you continue feeding your soul with delicious food without worrying about scrubbing afterwards. Wipe down the tile with a damp washcloth, and you&#8217;re done!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17100010\/dark-coloured-kitchen-backsplash-tiles.jpg\" alt=\"Dark coloured kitchen backsplash tiles which are easy to clean\" class=\"wp-image-48411\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17100010\/dark-coloured-kitchen-backsplash-tiles.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17100010\/dark-coloured-kitchen-backsplash-tiles-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17100010\/dark-coloured-kitchen-backsplash-tiles-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17100010\/dark-coloured-kitchen-backsplash-tiles-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Dark-coloured tiles are the best coverup for splatters <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Moisture Resistant Accent Tiles for Kitchen Backsplash&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Did you know the plumbing behind your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-wall-ideas\/\">kitchen walls <\/a>can lead to yellow stains and cracks over time? But there&#8217;s a way to make your walls last longer- and that&#8217;s with backsplash tiles. This stunning black and white monochrome pattern adds a luxe feel to the area, making your kitchen more functional for everyday use.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17100003\/moisture-resistant-kitchen-backsplash-tiles.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen backsplash tiles which are moisture resistant\" class=\"wp-image-48410\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17100003\/moisture-resistant-kitchen-backsplash-tiles.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17100003\/moisture-resistant-kitchen-backsplash-tiles-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17100003\/moisture-resistant-kitchen-backsplash-tiles-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17100003\/moisture-resistant-kitchen-backsplash-tiles-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Add tiles above the chimney to wipe grime easily<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Marble Tile Backsplash Kitchen Design&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>An aesthetically appealing kitchen infuses life into a home; after all, it is the one place that feeds the heart of a family. Think of a backsplash tile as the icing on the cake. With a home so impeccably designed, this marble backsplash design enhances the overall value of your home. You know what they say; your food absorbs emotions. The happier you feel cooking in a beautiful kitchen, the tastier the food is!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17095956\/marble-tile-kitchen-backsplash-design.jpg\" alt=\"Marble tile kitchen backsplash design  for an aesthetic look\" class=\"wp-image-48409\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17095956\/marble-tile-kitchen-backsplash-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17095956\/marble-tile-kitchen-backsplash-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17095956\/marble-tile-kitchen-backsplash-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17095956\/marble-tile-kitchen-backsplash-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Clean marble tile backsplash with warm soapy water<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Brick Tile Backsplash Kitchen Decor&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With so many design and colour options available today, finding something that suits your taste can feel overwhelming. In such cases, it is best to opt for neutral shades that complement the home, irrespective of the theme. This subway-inspired brick tile backsplash is fun but elegant at the same time. It complements the white and yellow cabinetry with its earthy tones, giving the space a sophisticated vibe.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17095948\/brick-tile-kitchen-backsplash-design.jpg\" alt=\"Brick tile kitchen backsplash for a fun and elegant look\" class=\"wp-image-48408\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17095948\/brick-tile-kitchen-backsplash-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17095948\/brick-tile-kitchen-backsplash-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17095948\/brick-tile-kitchen-backsplash-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17095948\/brick-tile-kitchen-backsplash-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Different shades of brown work well in a kitchen<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Affordable modular kitchen interiors with ample storage!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/08174049\/affordable-modular-kitchen-interiors-with-ample-storage.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Environment-Friendly Mosaic Tile Patterns for Kitchen Backsplash<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>It is not every day that you update your kitchen backsplash tiles, so why not go the extra mile to reduce your carbon footprint? Made from natural recycled materials, these mosaic tiles for kitchen backsplash are easy to manufacture and source for homes today. These tiles are even more cost-effective than other accent designs because of their low fuel consumption during manufacturing. A small step towards sustainability can make your kitchen more durable, functional, and appealing to the eyes.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17095942\/mosaic-tile-pattern-kitchen-backsplash.jpg\" alt=\"Mosaic tile patterns for kitchen backsplash which is environment friendly\" class=\"wp-image-48407\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17095942\/mosaic-tile-pattern-kitchen-backsplash.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17095942\/mosaic-tile-pattern-kitchen-backsplash-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17095942\/mosaic-tile-pattern-kitchen-backsplash-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/17095942\/mosaic-tile-pattern-kitchen-backsplash-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A quirky backsplash for this neutral-shaded kitchen<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Your kitchen is a busy place that needs a backsplash to reach your true MasterChef potential. No matter how carefully you cook or how earnestly you clean- these stunning kitchen backsplash tile designs will protect your wall from splashes and splatters, making everyday cleaning a breeze. Contact us at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">DesignCafe<\/a> for more such gorgeous <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/modern-kitchen-tiles\/\">tile designs for your home kitchen<\/a>.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs&nbsp;On Kitchen Backsplash Tile<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1. How do I choose the right tile for my kitchen backsplash?<\/strong><br>Follow these tips when choosing a tile for your kitchen backsplash:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Decide what you want as a focal point &#8211; cabinets or backsplash<\/li><li>Opt for timeless designs over trendy prints<\/li><li>Be open to shapes and textures for a modern vibe<\/li><li>Take time with selection; ask for samples<\/li><li>Choose easy-to-maintain stain-free tiles<\/li><li>Incorporate designs without space for grout; it makes cleaning a breeze<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2. Can I mix and match different tile types for a unique backsplash design?<\/strong><br>Yes, as long as you keep your choice of material consistent, mixing different types of tiles to create an aesthetic pattern is possible.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>3. Are there specific tile sizes or shapes that are commonly used for kitchen backsplashes?<\/strong><br>The most commonly used tile sizes for kitchen backsplash are 12&#215;24 and 24&#215;24 for larger blocks. Smaller pieces are often cut into 3&#215;6, 2&#215;6, and 2.5&#215;8 sizes. Shapes like squares, hexagons, subway tiles and brick-style tiles are popular for kitchens in modern homes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4. Are there any specific guidelines for positioning or height of a tile backsplash?<\/strong><br>Ideally, a standard kitchen backsplash height for Indian homes is 34 inches, with a 4-inch gap from the stovetop. However, you can extend the backsplash over your countertops for easy maintenance.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>5. Can I use different materials, such as glass or metal, for a backsplash instead of tile?<\/strong><br>Yes, materials like glass, metal, natural stone, and veneer can be used in place of tiles for your kitchen backsplash. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/glass-kitchen-backsplash-ideas\/\">Glass backsplashes<\/a> look more refined, versatile and are easy to maintain but come at a cost. In terms of pricing, tiles offer functionality on a budget.<\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Modular Kitchens At Best Prices<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Speak to our kitchen experts today!<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+91\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\